Level and changes, interpolated and extraplated

Source: R/data.R
ppts_easia_weuro_world_pchg.Rd

Level and changes, interpolated and extraplated

Usage

ppts_easia_weuro_world_pchg

Format

A data frame with 266 rows and 7 variables:

location_code

Short string code for country and regions

location_level

Country, or regional or sub-country

variable

Statistical variable

year_bins_type

The type of year binning

year_bins

Year bins given year binning

value

Level at start to end of bin

value_interp1

value with interpolation and extrapolation

pchg

Percentage change from start to end of bin

pchg_interp1

pchg with interpolation and extrapolation

Source

World bank, national statistics websites of W. Europe and E. Asia countries

Examples

data(ppts_easia_weuro_world_pchg)
print(ppts_easia_weuro_world_pchg)
